      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and represents a rare find for a discerning collector or enthusiast. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine, original state with no signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, the car performs exactly as it did when it first left the factory, supported by a comprehensive service history and meticulous upkeep. Every component, from the electronics to the undercarriage, has been maintained to the highest possible standards, making this one of the finest examples available on the market today.",
