    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly pristine, mint condition, having been meticulously cared for and stored in a climate-controlled environment. The paint retains its original showroom luster with no visible imperfections, and the interior is spotless, showing virtually no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, with all services up to date and a smooth, powerful performance that feels like new. This is a rare find for a collector or an enthusiast seeking the highest quality example available.",
