    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that hits the sweet spot of value and performance? This vehicle is in great shape and ready for its next adventure! It has been well-maintained and drives beautifully, showing only the minor signs of regular use you'd expect from a car that's been loved. It\u2019s a solid, dependable choice for anyone wanting a high-quality vehicle without the new-car price tag!",
